{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5ac151c1a3","title":"关于向归国华侨传达《中共中央通知》问题的补充通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"71b8f40dba","index":0,"year":1971,"month":11,"day":30,"articleId":"5ac151c1a3","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"f10c9d6647","name":"中共中央"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ef54a9947b","type":"title","text":"关于向归国华侨传达《中共中央通知》问题的补充通知","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5ac151c1a3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"96b2c74cb2","type":"paragraph","text":"中发 [1971]75号","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5ac151c1a3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7233361483","type":"paragraph","text":"各省、市、自治区党委，各大军区、各省军区、各野战军党委，军委各总部、各军、兵种党委，中央和国务院各部委领导小组、党的核心小组：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5ac151c1a3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5622fd17c6","type":"paragraph","text":"关于对久居国内有固定职业的归国华侨传达林陈反党集团问题，当时为了保密的需要，曾做了一些规定，这是必要的。但他们和当地工人一起工作和生活，由于传达和做法不一致，也引起一些意见，为了更好地把团结教育华侨的工作做好，中央作如下补充通知：","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5ac151c1a3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"822c2fc66a","type":"paragraph","text":"一、在中央[1971]69号文件下达前，已与当地职工一起听了传达的华侨，仍同职工一起学习讨论。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5ac151c1a3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7e39ea50f3","type":"paragraph","text":"二、尚未传达的单位，符合条件的，可同本单位的职工一起听传达和讨论。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5ac151c1a3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"56540cab57","type":"paragraph","text":"三、已单独组织华侨进行了三个文件传达的，可补充传达中发[1971]61号、62号、64号、67号四个文件。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5ac151c1a3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4615b81a02","type":"paragraph","text":" \t中共中央","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5ac151c1a3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"82ba3ed88a","type":"paragraph","text":"一九七一年十一月三十日","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5ac151c1a3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5338b43eea","type":"paragraph","text":"（此件发至县、团级）","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5ac151c1a3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"362cdf5adb","type":"paragraph","text":"____________________________________________________________________","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5ac151c1a3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"152c3f348e","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央办公厅 一九七一年十二月三日发出","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5ac151c1a3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b78b068a35","type":"paragraph","text":"____________________________________________________________________","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5ac151c1a3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ec76939e98","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：（根据中央文件原件打印）","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5ac151c1a3","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}